            <lg xml:id="TK219">
<l>nayaṉuṭaiyā ṉalkūrntā ṉātal ceyaṉīrmai</l>
<l>ceyyā tamaikalā vāṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The poverty of a benevolent man, is nothing but his inability to exercise the same.</l>
